<para style="q1">

<verse number="28" style="v" />Though they curse me, please bless me;</para>

<para style="q1">when they attack, may they be put to shame,</para>

<para style="q1">but may your servant rejoice.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="29" style="v" />May my adversaries be clothed with shame;</para>

<para style="q1">may they wear their shame like a robe.</para>
